=&amp;\left(N\sigma^2_N+N\mu_N^2\right)+x_{N+1}^2-(N+1)\mu_{N+1}^2\\
&amp;\text{by}\ (N+1)\mu_{N+1}=N\mu_N+x_{N+1}
